data.description: BETTER THAN NEW home in the desirable Belmont subdivision. Ready to host this spring and summer! Features a spacious open concept and split bedroom design that is perfect for families and entertainers. Also includes many upgrades: hardwood flooring on main level, fenced backyard, separate tub in master, covered patio, and much more. Enjoy the family-friendly neighborhood w/ private walking trails and lakes. Built only two years ago with several upgrades from owners. Zoned for Arlington Schools.
